  "cscw_dialogue": [
    {
      "turn_id": 1,
      "role": "Domain_Expert",
      "action_type": "propose",
      "utterance": "我们需要画一个ADSys的工作流程图，展示Ubuntu机器如何通过ADSys对接Active Directory控制器。核心参与方有三个：Ubuntu机器本身、ADSys中间件，还有后端的AD控制器。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "Ubuntu machine",
        "ADSys",
        "Active Directory controller"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 2,
      "role": "Diagram_Editor",
      "action_type": "clarify",
      "utterance": "明白，三个节点纵向排布吗？还有，Ubuntu机器是通过什么协议或方式触发整个流程的？",
      "elements_involved": [
        "Ubuntu machine"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 3,
      "role": "Domain_Expert",
      "action_type": "propose",
      "utterance": "对，从上到下。流程起点是Ubuntu机器上的adcli先向ADSys发起用户认证请求，然后ADSys再去AD控制器那里拉取GPO组策略。控制器返回解析好的相关GPO后，ADSys最后把策略解析并应用到Ubuntu机器上。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "adcli",
        "ADSys",
        "Active Directory controller",
        "authenticate user",
        "fetch GPOs",
        "relevant GPOs resolved",
        "parse GPOs and apply"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 4,
      "role": "Diagram_Editor",
      "action_type": "confirm",
      "utterance": "梳理一下：adcli→ADSys是\"authenticate user\"，ADSys→AD控制器是\"fetch GPOs\"，控制器返回是\"relevant GPOs resolved\"，最后ADSys→adcli是\"parse GPOs and apply\"。四条有向边，对吗？",
      "elements_involved": [
        "authenticate user",
        "fetch GPOs",
        "relevant GPOs resolved",
        "parse GPOs and apply"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 5,
      "role": "Domain_Expert",
      "action_type": "confirm",
      "utterance": "没错，就是这个闭环。对了，配色上我想用Ubuntu的品牌色系，主色调用那个橙红色，背景用淡紫灰，整体看起来专业又有辨识度。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "primaryColor",
        "primaryTextColor",
        "primaryBorderColor",
        "lineColor",
        "background",
        "secondaryColor"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 6,
      "role": "Diagram_Editor",
      "action_type": "execute",
      "utterance": "好的，我来绘制。三个节点纵向排列，adcli在上方，ADSys居中，AD控制器在底部，四条带标签的连线形成完整的工作流循环，配色按你说的Ubuntu风格处理。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "Ubuntu machine",
        "ADSys",
        "Active Directory controller",
        "authenticate user",
        "fetch GPOs",
        "relevant GPOs resolved",
        "parse GPOs and apply"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 7,
      "role": "Domain_Expert",
      "action_type": "repair",
      "utterance": "稍等，我注意到连线方向可能需要调整——控制器返回GPO的那条边应该是从AD控制器指向ADSys，表示数据回流，不是ADSys去拉取的状态。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "relevant GPOs resolved",
        "Active Directory controller",
        "ADSys"
      ],
      "is_repair": true
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 8,
      "role": "Diagram_Editor",
      "action_type": "execute",
      "utterance": "已修正，AD控制器→ADSys的\"relevant GPOs resolved\"箭头方向已调对。现在整个流程图逻辑完整了：认证→拉取策略→返回解析结果→应用配置，符合ADSys的实际工作机制。",
